type="local"
addr="jms-00M8">surjection</fr:link> from <fr:tex>A</fr:tex> to <fr:tex>\mathcal {P} { \mathopen {} \left ( A \right ) \mathclose {}}</fr:tex>.</fr:p>
 
   
   <fr:tree
xmlns:fr="http://www.jonmsterling.com/jms-005P.xml"
toc="false"
numbered="true"
